room_title: Escape room "Big Top Circus" by North Valley Escape Room in Phoenix
room_address: 42302 N Vision Way, Suite 104, Anthem, AZ 85086
room_description: Frederick the Great's wand is missing. The circus cannot go on without the magic show. Help Ziggy the Clown and his friends from the Freak Show to find the magic wand and save the day. You will find lots of fun and magic along your adventure. Truly an escape room like no other.
